00:09:38.778 --> 00:09:42.215 align:middle line:84%
in adult's sovereign
decisions about his or her body

00:09:42.215 --> 00:09:43.583 align:middle line:90%
and his or her consciousness.

00:09:43.583 --> 00:09:46.452 align:middle line:84%
And furthermore, I recognize
a cannabis can be a wonderful

00:09:46.452 --> 00:09:49.222 align:middle line:84%
healing agency for
many people and--

00:09:49.222 --> 00:09:51.024 align:middle line:90%
>> You just went overboard.

00:09:51.024 --> 00:09:52.225 align:middle line:90%
>> I went overboard.

00:09:52.225 --> 00:09:55.094 align:middle line:90%
I was-- I believe that cannabis

00:09:55.094 --> 00:09:57.564 align:middle line:84%
like all the sacred plants
should be treated with respect

00:09:57.564 --> 00:10:03.036 align:middle line:84%
and should not be smoked 16
hours a day, seven days a week.

00:10:03.036 --> 00:10:03.736 align:middle line:90%
And I got a--

00:10:03.736 --> 00:10:04.871 align:middle line:90%
>> You had a vaporizer.

00:10:04.871 --> 00:10:07.140 align:middle line:84%
>> I had a vaporizer,
