00:10:07.140 --> 00:10:09.509 align:middle line:84%
and no combustion products,
much better for the lungs.

00:10:09.509 --> 00:10:10.443 align:middle line:90%
>> You were serious.

00:10:10.443 --> 00:10:11.578 align:middle line:90%
>> I was serious.

00:10:11.578 --> 00:10:14.113 align:middle line:84%
I have three vaporizers
a matter of fact.

00:10:14.113 --> 00:10:17.917 align:middle line:84%
I was very committed to
my cannabis relationship.

00:10:17.917 --> 00:10:19.752 align:middle line:84%
>> I can't imagine the
world you were living in.

00:10:19.752 --> 00:10:22.322 align:middle line:90%
I was mostly doing that in--

00:10:22.322 --> 00:10:24.757 align:middle line:84%
for a period of time
when I was skiing and--

00:10:24.757 --> 00:10:25.692 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:10:25.692 --> 00:10:26.693 align:middle line:84%
>> -- having a lot
of fun outdoors,

00:10:26.693 --> 00:10:28.261 align:middle line:84%
and it was kind of
ragweed back then.

00:10:28.261 --> 00:10:29.062 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:10:29.062 --> 00:10:29.762 align:middle line:90%
>> But this sounds serious.

00:10:29.762 --> 00:10:30.363 align:middle line:90%
>> That's very strong--

00:10:30.363 --> 00:10:31.764 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:10:31.764 --> 00:10:32.832 align:middle line:84%
>> -- in how we're dealing with
very strong strains of cannabis,

00:10:32.832 --> 00:10:34.601 align:middle line:84%
and may be that was
part of the problem.

00:10:34.601 --> 00:10:37.737 align:middle line:84%
Cannabis, very, very heavily
focused of the THC end

00:10:37.737 --> 00:10:40.240 align:middle line:84%
of the ingredient,
less on the CBD

00:10:40.240 --> 00:10:43.009 align:middle line:84%
because cannabis has a
range of ingredients.

00:10:43.009 --> 00:10:43.443 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:10:43.443 --> 00:10:44.210 align:middle line:90%
>> And--

00:10:44.210 --> 00:10:44.978 align:middle line:90%
>> That creates paranoia.

00:10:44.978 --> 00:10:45.812 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, it's well-known.

00:10:45.812 --> 00:10:46.846 align:middle line:90%
>> And that's what I noticed.

00:10:46.846 --> 00:10:48.014 align:middle line:84%
>> And that was one
of my problems was

00:10:48.014 --> 00:10:51.217 align:middle line:84%
that I became paranoid,
suspicious, jealous.

00:10:51.217 --> 00:10:52.585 align:middle line:90%
I didn't trust anybody.

00:10:52.585 --> 00:10:56.389 align:middle line:84%
I behaved negatively
towards my wonderful wife

00:10:56.389 --> 00:10:58.758 align:middle line:90%
and partner Santha.

00:10:58.758 --> 00:11:00.193 align:middle line:84%
>> You were in the
prison of your own making.

00:11:00.193 --> 00:11:02.996 align:middle line:84%
>> There was lots of ways by
which I was refusing to admit.

00:11:02.996 --> 00:11:05.665 align:middle line:84%
And from the moment
that I started drinking,

00:11:05.665 --> 00:11:10.303 align:middle line:84%
I was which was in 2003, I
did start to get messages

00:11:10.303 --> 00:11:13.072 align:middle line:84%
that I needed to do something
about my cannabis habit

00:11:13.072 --> 00:11:15.141 align:middle line:90%
and would even feel really bad

00:11:15.141 --> 00:11:17.577 align:middle line:84%
about that during
the session itself,

00:11:17.577 --> 00:11:21.047 align:middle line:84%
but I kept going
back to the habit.

00:11:21.047 --> 00:11:24.550 align:middle line:84%
And it was only in 2011 when
I was already up to something

00:11:24.550 --> 00:11:28.421 align:middle line:84%
like 35, 40 Ayahuasca sessions
and I went down to Brazil

00:11:28.421 --> 00:11:30.289 align:middle line:90%
for five sessions that's--

00:11:30.289 --> 00:11:34.327 align:middle line:84%
and I shall continue to call her
Mother Ayahuasca whether she's

00:11:34.327 --> 00:11:35.728 align:middle line:90%
real or not.

00:11:35.728 --> 00:11:40.633 align:middle line:84%
Mother Ayahuasca focused on my
cannabis problem and showed me

00:11:40.633 --> 00:11:44.937 align:middle line:84%
that I was moving in the
wrong direction in my life

00:11:44.937 --> 00:11:49.075 align:middle line:84%
and that I was poised
on the edge of an abyss.

00:11:49.075 --> 00:11:53.012 align:middle line:84%
And that if I continue to allow
my behavior to deteriorate

00:11:53.012 --> 00:11:57.483 align:middle line:84%
in the way that it was doing
because of my abuse of cannabis,

00:11:57.483 --> 00:11:59.585 align:middle line:90%
there would be some sense

00:11:59.585 --> 00:12:04.557 align:middle line:84%
in which I might be immortally
doomed that I could not--

00:12:04.557 --> 00:12:09.896 align:middle line:84%
that I could not put right the
wrongs and the pain and the hurt

00:12:09.896 --> 00:12:11.898 align:middle line:90%
that my behavior was causing.

00:12:11.898 --> 00:12:16.569 align:middle line:84%
So, in a way Mother
Ayahuasca took me to hell.

00:12:16.569 --> 00:12:18.571 align:middle line:84%
And I'm not claiming
that hell is real either.

00:12:18.571 --> 00:12:20.306 align:middle line:90%
>> It was your experience.

00:12:20.306 --> 00:12:24.877 align:middle line:84%
>> But I was taken to a place
and shown very, very vividly,

00:12:24.877 --> 00:12:26.713 align:middle line:90%
this is what you will face

00:12:26.713 --> 00:12:29.482 align:middle line:84%
if you don't fix this
problem in your life.

00:12:29.482 --> 00:12:31.017 align:middle line:90%
>> What did that look like?

00:12:31.017 --> 00:12:34.420 align:middle line:84%
>> It looked like something out
of Hieronymus Bosch, you know.

00:12:34.420 --> 00:12:37.389 align:middle line:84%
Hieronymus Bosch was a
visionary artist of the 1400s

00:12:37.389 --> 00:12:40.793 align:middle line:84%
and he painted hell a number of
times and it looked like that.

00:12:40.793 --> 00:12:41.994 align:middle line:90%
And it looked a little bit

00:12:41.994 --> 00:12:45.298 align:middle line:84%
like the Ancient Egyptian
Judgment Hall of Osiris

00:12:45.298 --> 00:12:47.734 align:middle line:84%
where every action, every
thought, every deed,

00:12:47.734 --> 00:12:49.469 align:middle line:90%
every moment of your life is--

00:12:49.469 --> 00:12:52.405 align:middle line:84%
becomes transparent and
you must account for it.

00:12:52.405 --> 00:12:55.875 align:middle line:84%
And I found that where the
heart is wade and the scales

00:12:55.875 --> 00:12:57.543 align:middle line:90%
against the feather truth.

00:12:57.543 --> 00:13:02.749 align:middle line:84%
And I found that the bending
out of shape of my behavior,

00:13:02.749 --> 00:13:05.818 align:middle line:84%
of my attitude to the
world that was linked to,

00:13:05.818 --> 00:13:08.421 align:middle line:84%
I would not say it was caused
by cannabis, but was linked

00:13:08.421 --> 00:13:10.990 align:middle line:84%
to cannabis would put me
in a place of jeopardy

00:13:10.990 --> 00:13:14.794 align:middle line:84%
in the judgment hall and that
my heart would not weigh light

00:13:14.794 --> 00:13:16.062 align:middle line:90%
against the feather.

00:13:16.062 --> 00:13:18.831 align:middle line:84%
And this was an alarming
situation for me.

00:13:18.831 --> 00:13:21.200 align:middle line:84%
There were elements
of those experiences,

00:13:21.200 --> 00:13:22.668 align:middle line:90%
those five experiences in Brazil

00:13:22.668 --> 00:13:25.071 align:middle line:84%
which are too painful
for me to recount.

00:13:25.071 --> 00:13:27.874 align:middle line:84%
But the net result is
that when I came back

00:13:27.874 --> 00:13:29.742 align:middle line:90%
to England, I was done.

00:13:29.742 --> 00:13:31.177 align:middle line:90%
>> And that was 2011.

00:13:31.177 --> 00:13:32.278 align:middle line:90%
>> And that was 2011.

00:13:32.278 --> 00:13:33.513 align:middle line:90%
I was done with cannabis

00:13:33.513 --> 00:13:36.014 align:middle line:84%
and I have never
smoked it against since.

00:13:36.014 --> 00:13:41.320 align:middle line:84%
And for me, it has been
a wonderful revelation.

00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:42.288 align:middle line:90%
So--

00:13:42.288 --> 00:13:43.489 align:middle line:84%
>> What did you discover
in yourself

00:13:43.489 --> 00:13:45.258 align:middle line:84%
when that was no
longer clouding you?

00:13:45.258 --> 00:13:47.026 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, first of all,
what I discovered is

00:13:47.026 --> 00:13:48.861 align:middle line:84%
that all the pain--
'cause it was--

00:13:48.861 --> 00:13:52.131 align:middle line:84%
jealousy and suspicion were
causing me pain as well as--

00:13:52.131 --> 00:13:52.899 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:13:52.899 --> 00:13:55.334 align:middle line:90%
>> -- causing others pain.

00:13:55.334 --> 00:13:56.602 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:13:56.602 --> 00:13:59.071 align:middle line:84%
>> And the first-- so that
just vanished completely.

00:13:59.071 --> 00:14:00.206 align:middle line:90%
I don't approach life.

00:14:00.206 --> 00:14:01.874 align:middle line:90%
I don't approach the world.

00:14:01.874 --> 00:14:03.643 align:middle line:90%
I don't approach my wife.

00:14:03.643 --> 00:14:06.412 align:middle line:84%
I don't approach
anybody I meet in a state

00:14:06.412 --> 00:14:08.581 align:middle line:90%
of suspicion or mistrust.

00:14:08.581 --> 00:14:11.484 align:middle line:90%
I come from a place of trust.

00:14:11.484 --> 00:14:13.886 align:middle line:84%
And I would rather
trust people now

00:14:13.886 --> 00:14:17.590 align:middle line:84%
and perhaps be proved
wrong than mistrust them.

00:14:17.590 --> 00:14:18.191 align:middle line:90%
I don't like--

00:14:18.191 --> 00:14:19.125 align:middle line:90%
>> Too painful.

00:14:19.125 --> 00:14:20.059 align:middle line:84%
>> -- being in a
place of mistrust.

00:14:20.059 --> 00:14:20.793 align:middle line:90%
It's much too painful.

00:14:20.793 --> 00:14:21.627 align:middle line:90%
All of that is gone.

00:14:21.627 --> 00:14:24.096 align:middle line:90%
I have absolutely no paranoia.

00:14:24.096 --> 00:14:25.631 align:middle line:90%
I have no suspicion.

00:14:25.631 --> 00:14:28.367 align:middle line:84%
I feel very comfortable
inside my own skin.

00:14:28.367 --> 00:14:32.205 align:middle line:84%
And I don't elaborate
fantasies to worry about.

00:14:32.205 --> 00:14:35.775 align:middle line:84%
I feel much more-- much, much
happier and much more relaxed.

00:14:35.775 --> 00:14:38.010 align:middle line:84%
And the big thing that was
worried me about cannabis

00:14:38.010 --> 00:14:39.679 align:middle line:90%
which was that if I stopped it,

00:14:39.679 --> 00:14:41.747 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't be able
to write my books.

00:14:41.747 --> 00:14:44.417 align:middle line:84%
That turned out to
be total nonsense.

00:14:44.417 --> 00:14:47.887 align:middle line:84%
And that far from
becoming less productive

00:14:47.887 --> 00:14:49.322 align:middle line:84%
since I stopped smoking
cannabis,

00:14:49.322 --> 00:14:51.389 align:middle line:84%
I've become much
more productive--

00:14:51.389 --> 00:14:52.358 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, and I--

00:14:52.358 --> 00:14:53.726 align:middle line:84%
>> -- and like much
more fluently.

00:14:53.726 --> 00:14:56.128 align:middle line:84%
>> But at the same time, during
the years you were smoking,

00:14:56.128 --> 00:14:58.464 align:middle line:90%
you were cranking out books.

00:14:58.464 --> 00:15:00.132 align:middle line:84%
It's like people
listening to this would say,

00:15:00.132 --> 00:15:01.567 align:middle line:90%
"How is that possible?

00:15:01.567 --> 00:15:03.536 align:middle line:84%
Those books were brilliant
and there were lots

00:15:03.536 --> 00:15:04.670 align:middle line:90%
of it, dozen of them or so."

00:15:04.670 --> 00:15:05.938 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah, I was cranking
up books.

00:15:05.938 --> 00:15:07.306 align:middle line:90%
And they were good books.

00:15:07.306 --> 00:15:08.107 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, they were.

00:15:08.107 --> 00:15:09.108 align:middle line:90%
>> I would love to tell you.

00:15:09.108 --> 00:15:10.710 align:middle line:90%
I was focused with cannabis.

00:15:10.710 --> 00:15:12.612 align:middle line:90%
It would put me into dreamland.

00:15:12.612 --> 00:15:15.281 align:middle line:90%
I was able to work with it.

00:15:15.281 --> 00:15:18.451 align:middle line:84%
But I'll tell you what
sometimes would happen which is

00:15:18.451 --> 00:15:22.655 align:middle line:84%
that sometimes I would
spend an entire day puzzling

00:15:22.655 --> 00:15:24.991 align:middle line:90%
over a three-line paragraph.

00:15:24.991 --> 00:15:26.292 align:middle line:90%
Slowed me down as well.

00:15:26.292 --> 00:15:27.593 align:middle line:90%
>> I see, yes.

00:15:27.593 --> 00:15:31.564 align:middle line:84%
>> And sometimes, I think
the books got a bit overlong

00:15:31.564 --> 00:15:35.001 align:middle line:84%
because of that process
in a weird kind of way

00:15:35.001 --> 00:15:37.003 align:middle line:84%
that I would kind of keep
coming back in [inaudible].

00:15:37.003 --> 00:15:38.271 align:middle line:90%
>> Kind of felt heavy.

00:15:38.271 --> 00:15:39.372 align:middle line:90%
>> A little bit heavy.

00:15:39.372 --> 00:15:41.540 align:middle line:90%
And that's what's changed.

00:15:41.540 --> 00:15:43.943 align:middle line:84%
And also I'm just
much more productive

00:15:43.943 --> 00:15:47.013 align:middle line:84%
and I'm finding myself
exploring realms of ideas

00:15:47.013 --> 00:15:49.649 align:middle line:84%
that I actually didn't
explore before.

00:15:49.649 --> 00:15:52.351 align:middle line:84%
I feel that I've opened
up a lot since then.

00:15:52.351 --> 00:15:55.488 align:middle line:84%
So I feel that I've had a
monkey taken off my back.

00:15:55.488 --> 00:15:57.990 align:middle line:84%
And again, I want to
emphasize, because I don't want

00:15:57.990 --> 00:16:01.627 align:middle line:84%
to be misunderstood on this, I
am not putting cannabis down.

00:16:01.627 --> 00:16:03.229 align:middle line:90%
>> Right, I understand.

00:16:03.229 --> 00:16:06.365 align:middle line:84%
>> Cannabis is, for many people,
an incredibly helpful aid.

00:16:06.365 --> 00:16:09.068 align:middle line:90%
And there was a time in my life

00:16:09.068 --> 00:16:10.870 align:middle line:84%
when it was incredibly
helpful for me.

00:16:10.870 --> 00:16:14.840 align:middle line:84%
My problem was the
self-indulgent abuse--

00:16:14.840 --> 00:16:15.608 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:16:15.608 --> 00:16:16.309 align:middle line:90%
>> -- of this sacred word.

00:16:16.309 --> 00:16:17.510 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, I understand.

00:16:17.510 --> 00:16:18.611 align:middle line:84%
What I'm wondering, though
you were talking about--

00:16:18.611 --> 00:16:20.479 align:middle line:84%
I was talking about
ragweed from, you know,

00:16:20.479 --> 00:16:23.115 align:middle line:84%
a few decades ago and
then what has become now

00:16:23.115 --> 00:16:25.985 align:middle line:84%
with this super-hybridized
and specialized product.

00:16:25.985 --> 00:16:27.186 align:middle line:90%
>> That's what I was smoking.

00:16:27.186 --> 00:16:29.889 align:middle line:84%
>> And that, you said
there is a chemical shift

00:16:29.889 --> 00:16:31.057 align:middle line:90%
from one chemical element--

00:16:31.057 --> 00:16:31.824 align:middle line:90%
>> Well there are--

00:16:31.824 --> 00:16:33.159 align:middle line:90%
>> -- to the other.

00:16:33.159 --> 00:16:36.662 align:middle line:84%
>> Yes, there are two key
ingredients in cannabis and one

00:16:36.662 --> 00:16:40.333 align:middle line:84%
