I think really what was lay

00:34:37.342 --> 00:34:42.013 align:middle line:84%
at the heart of this was that
there is a powerful lobby

00:34:42.013 --> 00:34:47.084 align:middle line:84%
within science which is involved
in materialist reductionism

00:34:47.084 --> 00:34:50.188 align:middle line:84%
that they want to reduce
everything to matter.

00:34:50.188 --> 00:34:52.923 align:middle line:84%
And this is actually not
a lobby that is based

00:34:52.923 --> 00:34:55.994 align:middle line:84%
on experimental evidence
or a scientific fact.

00:34:55.994 --> 00:34:57.996 align:middle line:84%
It's actually, if you
really examine it closely,

00:34:57.996 --> 00:35:01.132 align:middle line:84%
it's a belief system that
everything may be reduced

00:35:01.132 --> 00:35:04.002 align:middle line:84%
to matter, you know, to
physical aspect of us.

00:35:04.002 --> 00:35:06.471 align:middle line:84%
So therefore, in this
particular view of science

00:35:06.471 --> 00:35:10.408 align:middle line:84%
which is a reference frame, not
a fact, in this particular view

00:35:10.408 --> 00:35:14.846 align:middle line:84%
of science, consciousness is,
and this is how they defined it,

00:35:14.846 --> 00:35:17.315 align:middle line:84%
an epiphenomenon
of brain activity.

00:35:17.315 --> 00:35:19.451 align:middle line:84%
In other words, from the
materialist point of view,

00:35:19.451 --> 00:35:23.788 align:middle line:84%
consciousness is a kind of
accident of material processes,

00:35:23.788 --> 00:35:26.424 align:middle line:84%
that our brains have
to do certain stuff

00:35:26.424 --> 00:35:30.195 align:middle line:84%
so that we can function like
this sort of meat robots

00:35:30.195 --> 00:35:32.197 align:middle line:90%
in the physical realm.

00:35:32.197 --> 00:35:34.933 align:middle line:84%
And because some of that
stuff is complicated,

00:35:34.933 --> 00:35:38.770 align:middle line:84%
accidentally this thing called
consciousness has a reason.

