It is produced.

00:35:39.604 --> 00:35:41.372 align:middle line:90%
It is generated by the brain.

00:35:41.372 --> 00:35:45.176 align:middle line:84%
And from the materialist
point of view, when we die,

00:35:45.176 --> 00:35:47.178 align:middle line:84%
