consciousness

00:35:47.178 --> 00:35:49.414 align:middle line:84%
and that is the end
of our story.

00:35:49.414 --> 00:35:52.984 align:middle line:84%
And many scientific materialists
mistake their personal belief

00:35:52.984 --> 00:35:56.287 align:middle line:84%
