00:42:37.321 --> 00:42:39.357 align:middle line:90%
You know, for a long time,

00:42:39.357 --> 00:42:44.161 align:middle line:84%
we had the Ptolemaic
reference frame.

00:42:44.161 --> 00:42:47.098 align:middle line:90%
In Ptolemaic astronomy,

00:42:47.098 --> 00:42:50.601 align:middle line:84%
the earth was the
center of everything.

00:42:50.601 --> 00:42:53.838 align:middle line:84%
And it was thought that the
sun revolved around the earth,

00:42:53.838 --> 00:42:55.940 align:middle line:84%
and the stars revolved
around the earth,

00:42:55.940 --> 00:42:58.109 align:middle line:84%
and the planets revolved around
the earth, everything was

00:42:58.109 --> 00:43:00.111 align:middle line:84%
in the center-- the
earth was in the center,

00:43:00.111 --> 00:43:03.648 align:middle line:84%
and the earth stayed still,
the earth did not move.

00:43:03.648 --> 00:43:05.116 align:middle line:84%
This was the Ptolemaic
reference frame.

00:43:05.116 --> 00:43:08.286 align:middle line:84%
And the Ptolemaic reference
frame dominated early science

00:43:08.286 --> 00:43:10.621 align:middle line:84%
for a very long time,
you know, from the time

00:43:10.621 --> 00:43:13.758 align:middle line:84%
of the library of-- when Ptolemy
himself worked in the Library

00:43:13.758 --> 00:43:18.229 align:middle line:84%
of Alexandria right through
until the 16th century.

00:43:18.229 --> 00:43:22.366 align:middle line:84%
And gradually, as new-- even
later than the 16th century.

00:43:22.366 --> 00:43:26.070 align:middle line:84%
Gradually as new evidence
began to come into place,

00:43:26.070 --> 00:43:28.573 align:middle line:84%
it was troubling-- the
evidence was troubling

00:43:28.573 --> 00:43:31.142 align:middle line:84%
for the earth-centered
reference frame.

00:43:31.142 --> 00:43:33.411 align:middle line:84%
And what the scientist at that
time would do was they would

00:43:33.411 --> 00:43:36.647 align:middle line:84%
invent patches and
fixes, so-called epicycles

00:43:36.647 --> 00:43:38.849 align:middle line:84%
which explained the
way the new evidence.

00:43:38.849 --> 00:43:42.687 align:middle line:84%
And in fact, if you opposed
the Ptolemaic method,

00:43:42.687 --> 00:43:48.092 align:middle line:84%
if you dare to say that actually
the sun was at the center

00:43:48.092 --> 00:43:50.828 align:middle line:84%
and the earth revolved
around the sun,

00:43:50.828 --> 00:43:52.296 align:middle line:84%
you could get burnt
at the stake.

00:43:52.296 --> 00:43:55.232 align:middle line:84%
And that's rather
like what we have now

00:43:55.232 --> 00:43:57.501 align:middle line:84%
with the materialist
reference frame in science.

00:43:57.501 --> 00:43:59.570 align:middle line:84%
Of course, people don't actually
get burnt at the stake to death.

